  "text": "Remark 1.7. In the symmetric case λ = 1, the formula (1.76), up to a rescaling, was derived by the current authors from a model of nonintersecting paths on the circle [CITATION_1] . That model was not robust enough to produce the asymmetric tacnode kernel, and the above theorem is new for λ = 1.",
